text: Vanessa Morgan Mziray (born March 23, 1992), known professionally as Vanessa Morgan is a Canadian actress. She acts mostly on television. She played Sarah in My Babysitter's a Vampire and Amanda on the Family Channel show The Latest Buzz. Morgan was born in Ottawa, Ontario. ==References== Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Ottawa
